name: Alliance Tournament IX: Darkside.
description: Newcomers a year before in the Eighth Alliance Tournament, <url=showinfo:16159//605845106>DarkSide.</url> had quickly made a name for themselves with a quarter-final performance that year. In the Ninth Alliance Tournament they catapulted themselves into Tournament history by ending the reign of <url=showinfo:16159//386292982>Pandemic Legion</url> and knocking them out in convincing fashion. In one fell swoop they blew the Tournament field wide open and made <url=showinfo:1378//717397234>Shadoo</url> the happiest man in the world.
group_name: Tournament Cards: Alliance Tournament All Stars
